msgstr ""

#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "locations"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Create areas or locations and organize them as hierarchical tags. The pipe “|” character can be used to insert a new level (a group of locations).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "A location is shown as a shape on the map when selected. Initially each location will be represented as a square or circle and can be changed to a rectangle or ellipse by adjusting the shape's width and/or height. Each location is stored as tag entry under the geotagging collection.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shape\n"
": Select the circle or rectangle symbol to choose the default shape for new locations.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"new location / new sub-location\n"
": When no location is selected the _new location_ button lets you create a location at root level. When a location is selected the _new sub-location_ button lets you create a sub-location within the selected location.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"show all\n"
": Show or hide all locations that are visible on the current map.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "actions on the locations list"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"click\n"
": Select (or de-select) a location. If the location is not visible on the map, the map is automatically centred on that location.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Ctrl+click\n"
": Edit the name of the location. Press Enter to save changes or Esc to close the editing window without saving.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"right-click\n"
": Call up a sub-menu which allows you to:\n"
": - Edit the name of the location.\n"
": - Delete the location.\n"
": - Update the filmstrip -- the filmstrip will be populated all images within the selected location.\n"
": - Switch to the lighttable view and show a collection that contains all the images within the selected location.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "actions on locations in the map"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"click and drag\n"
": Move the location shape to a new position on the map.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Ctrl+click or Ctrl+Shift+click\n"
": Move an image or a group of images to place them inside a location shape.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"mouse scroll\n"
": When inside a location shape (but not over an image), increase or decrease the size of that shape.\n"
": When hovering over an image, display the different thumbnails of images located at that position on the map.\n"
": When outside a location shape (and not over an image) zoom the map in or out.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Shift+scroll\n"
": Increase or decrease the width of the location shape.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Ctrl+scroll\n"
": Increase or decrease the height of the location shape.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"click on a location shape\n"
": Select a different location when the _show all_ checkbox is selected.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/lighttable/select.md
#, no-wrap
