#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/darkroom/duplicate-manager.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "duplicate manager"
msgstr "менеджер дублікатів"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/darkroom/duplicate-manager.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "The duplicate manager lists all versions of the current darkroom image with their preview thumbnails. Hold down the left mouse button on a thumbnail to temporarily show that version in the center view. Double click to switch to this version and edit it. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/darkroom/duplicate-manager.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "The buttons on the top-right allow you to create new duplicates of the current image. You can either create a 'virgin' version (with an empty history stack) or an exact duplicate of the current image. For your convenience, you can also assign a name to each version.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/darkroom/duplicate-manager.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "The displayed name is stored in the _version name_ metadata tag, which can also be edited within the [metadata editor](../shared/metadata-editor.md) module.\n"
