#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/darkroom/module-order.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"custom\n"
": Since darktable 3.0, it is possible to change the order in which modules are applied in the pixelpipe by clicking on the module header while holding Ctrl+Shift and dragging it into a new position. If you have changed the order of any modules, this parameter will show the value \"custom\".\n"
