#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/darkroom/module-order.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "It is possible to reset the module order back to the v3.0 default order by clicking on the _reset parameters_ icon on the _module order_ header. You can also use the _presets menu_ to change the ordering to either v3.0 default or to legacy ordering.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/darkroom/module-order.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "For a list of the default module orders, please refer to the [default module order](../../../special-topics/module-order.md) section.\n"
msgstr ""

