"[processing modules](./processing-modules/_index.md)\n"
": These modules are used exclusively in the darkroom view, and each performs its processing operation on the image before passing the image up to the next module for further processing. Together this sequence of processing steps forms the [pixelpipe](../darkroom/pixelpipe/the-pixelpipe-and-module-order.md).\n"
