#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "It can be rather tedious to create a drawn mask which precisely covers a particular feature in an image. In this example, we want to enhance the color contrast of the lion sculpture shown in the left image above without affecting the background.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#: content/darkroom/masking-and-blending/masks/refinement-controls.md
